data.description: Step into the perfect blend of comfort and style at 5210 Sunbeam Ave! This charming residence is a dream come true for first-time homebuyers, those seeking a cozy downsizing option, or savvy investors looking for the ideal spot. Boasting 3 bedrooms and 1 full bath, this home exudes warmth with its original hardwood floors, seamlessly blending the allure of classic features with contemporary updates.A highlight of this property is the brand-new HVAC system, ensuring your comfort year-round. Picture yourself relaxing in the cozy embrace of the screened-in porch, accessed through elegant French doors, providing a perfect spot for morning coffee or evening unwinding. Beyond, a level and spacious fenced backyard offer a private oasis for entertaining or enjoying the outdoors. Convenience is at your doorstep with this home's central location, making it easy to access everything you need. From local amenities to essential services, you'll find it all just moments away. Whether you're a first-time buyer, down-sizer, or investor, 5210 Sunbeam Ave ticks all the boxes. Embark on a journey of discovery and schedule your private tour today. Witness firsthand the timeless charm and modern appeal that make this property a standout in the market. Don't miss the chance to call 5210 Sunbeam Ave your new home!
